Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S{\fn微软雅黑}{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}{\fn}mekh復活的時刻到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(300,0)\c&H0700BE&}我們的Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的盛典開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面對如此巨大的玩意人類能幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見一來看…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待著這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh不是壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被我封印起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君回應了我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君再也不是別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也不是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後只剩下解開皆水之封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh能走到零空間之外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君將成為這個星球的王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球將成為諏訪君的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德 這就是你翹首以盼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是這個星球最後的盛典了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.21,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3}本片字幕由異域字幕組(www.yydm.com)製作,僅供試看之用,如果喜歡本作品,請購買並支持正版!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想利用Cybody成為世界支配者的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.39,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3}翻譯 M熊 SX 校譯 S 時間 倉鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有任何意義的 少癡心妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底你也不過是個墜入情網的天真少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你這點倒是很可愛喲 Everonu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我被這個Cybody Sympathy拒絕這麼久是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？ 你做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個Sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠和其他的Cybody一起使用Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實只有新籐諏訪才能對S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh使用Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可以將這個新籐諏訪和S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh都據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他將永遠活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我操縱S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh的零件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把諏訪還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}喂喂 人家未婚妻在旁邊看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一樣被同一個人授以雙刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要決一死戰麼 道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河十字斬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh已如我的手足一般了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和現在的我戰鬥就如同跟S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh戰鬥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們還不知道S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh的真正力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些巫女的話 或許已經察覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒後的S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh 現在正飢渴難耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正激動不已於吸收復活所需的慾望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而阻擋這些的正是零空間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零空間的封印解開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh會為了變成原來的Cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會把這個星球所有的慾望都吸食殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 這個星球就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh的容量來算的話 這種可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說人類會滅亡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類都滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便把S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh得到了 你又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開了皆水之封印 到達了第五階段的S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自由的操縱時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且成為了Star Driver的我將如時間旅行者一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以隨心所欲的往返於喜歡的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後的未來可就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把所有的東西都奪回來 涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續掠奪嗎 時生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急會議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德的行為違反綺羅星協議第11條
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 對其予以除籍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群沒大腦的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將迎來啟程之日的只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都不過是我為了獲得S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh而用之則棄的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼綺羅星 可笑至極
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個煩死人的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特納西家的Cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水的Cybody嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然能從神殿中出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 對我來說正是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束了 道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的手上S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh還可以這樣用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你搞的那些破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的Cybody現在都成了S{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh的道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的heigent竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的輪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始將是只屬於我的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恆之夢即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 還能承受多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特納西君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 最終我們還是被利用了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類跟Cybody扯上關係本身就是個錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為…不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許對我們來說可能還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是cybody是我們到達未來的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這一次那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德錯誤地使用了cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh成為了錯誤的cybody而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼…在說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說？誰在說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dajethos…在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有了…印記…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺失的印記難道復甦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yodck在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也在…呼喚我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們身上還殘留著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bafaro Cross
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法返回原樣的cybody們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘劍 神吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團的善後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們來處理 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃脫了s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh的束縛後開始行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群囚牢之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等強大的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼強大的東西要怎麼樣才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為得勢了就能夠為所欲為的這股年青的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這壓倒性的力量面前也只能面對現實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠…看得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能夠…看得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然孤身一人就衝進s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在無盡的藍色黑暗中懷著自己的迷惘被粉碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼盛典就到此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王之柱…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪打算封印s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算讓s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道諏訪是為了封印s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh而進入其中的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…地球卻被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一仗沒白打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅長表演被確定的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有保護好和子的自信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初就打算這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兒子和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠看到別人看不到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底他看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你這樣的人已經看不到的東西罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪喜歡的還是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事情和該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零空間要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼一瞬間我真被嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但服從塔科特是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會就這麼放下諏訪不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從相遇的那一刻起 你就一直讓我們充滿歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那才是你的第一階段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我最近一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是沒有見到你會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果沒有來到島上那該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特認為在心中一直想著自己認準的那個人就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特別羨慕找到男朋友的琉裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否能真正體會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時深深地喜歡上兩個男生這種內心的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種伎倆是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,s{\fn微软雅黑}ā{\fn}mekh喲 我能夠看見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「保護柔弱小盆友」可是我的家規
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們以後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會看到與此不同 更美的天空
